SALVATORE FERRAGAMO: STORIE DI SETA 😍
__
Tailor your own fragrance with @ferragamo Storie Di Seta 🌿💐🌹🌸🍂
The collection consists of four variants and a booster set which gives you infinite choices to create and layer your own scent!

Giardini di Seta where crunchy juicy red fruits dive into transparent floral bright musks🌸

Giungle di Seta where wild green freshness develops on a pure universal woodiness🍃

Savane di Seta where a splash of a funny yellow vegetable is blended with a sophisticated cologne structure🍁

Oceani di Seta where crystallized spicy & salty freshness intertwines with vapors of flowers and woods🌊

Musky and Woody Boosters for a second skin effect.

The four EDPs  are designed to be worn alone or can be layered with any other scent and booster from the collection for a unique bespoke experience, unveiling  unexplored emotions that appeal to every sense.
